      <p><strong>Business Information:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Business Name:</strong> Shri Govind Pharmacy</li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> Near Main Bus Stand, Sikar, Rajasthan – 332001</li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> +91 98765 43210 | info@shrigovindpharmacy.com</li>
        <li><strong>Business Hours:</strong> Mon–Sat: 8 AM – 9 PM, Sunday: 9 AM – 6 PM</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

